WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
In addition to your application, all candidates are required to have a valid passport

00:03.000 --> 00:08.000
If you are chosen to participate in a Candidate Weekend, you will need to be able to travel to Abu Dhabi

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
